WEBVTT

1
00:51:01.170 --> 00:51:03.130 
我以为我们已经无话可说了
I really thought we were done with this.

2
00:51:03.190 --> 00:51:04.970 
最后一次谈话
One last conversation.

3
00:51:05.070 --> 00:51:06.590 
最后一个请求
One last ask?

4
00:51:08.610 --> 00:51:10.540 
你是希望我不去出席医委会的听证会
Are you hoping I just don't show up to the Med Board

5
00:51:10.540 --> 00:51:12.540 
还是你让我别去
or are you going to ask me not to?

6
00:51:13.810 --> 00:51:15.040 
无所谓
Whichever.

7
00:51:15.300 --> 00:51:16.930 
我想说的是
Look. All I want to say is:

8
00:51:20.120 --> 00:51:21.370 
对不起
I'm sorry.

9
00:51:22.440 --> 00:51:26.120 
真的很抱歉
I am truly sorry.

10
00:51:26.950 --> 00:51:29.620 
说不好是出于复仇
Some kind of desire for revenge,

11
00:51:29.620 --> 00:51:33.100 
还是好胜  或者嗜血的欲望
or competitiveness, or bloodlust

